---
title: Spicy Shakshuka with Chickpeas, Feta Cheese, and Chili Flakes
description: Shakshuka is the ultimate eggs-for-dinner meal. In this Israeli staple, eggs are poached directly in the protein-packed sauce but not cooked all the way through. After all, you need some runny yolk to dip that toast into!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-shakshuka-with-chickpeas-950afb58.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spicy-shakshuka-with-chickpeas-13275fa9.pdf
